cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.GR 

This paper discusses the convergence of GAN training, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and graphics (cs.GR). The paper specifically focuses on regularization strategies for GAN training, which is a common technique used in machine learning and computer vision. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG and cs.CV, followed by cs.AI, cs.NE, and cs.GR.
